<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0424b04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424b05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424b06" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1306</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0424b07" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0424034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】久安四年寫仁和寺藏本，【乙】久安五年寫高山寺藏本，【丙】文和二年寫高野山寶壽院藏本</note>北斗七星護摩祕要儀<note n="0424035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">軌＋（一卷）【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0424035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">軌【大】，軌一卷【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424035"><lem wit="【大】">軌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">軌一卷</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0424b08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424b09" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="author">大興善寺翻經院灌頂阿闍梨述</byline>
<lb n="0424b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0424b1001"><note n="0424036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（或本佛言）＋我【丙】</note><note n="0424036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我【大】，或本佛言我【丙】</note><app n="0424036"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">或本佛言我</rdg></app>今為末世薄福眾生故。說是北極七星供
<lb n="0424b11" ed="T"/>養護摩次第儀則。於<note n="0424037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">靜＝淨ィ【甲】</note><note n="0424037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">靜【大】，淨【校異-甲】</note><app n="0424037"><lem wit="【大】">靜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">淨</rdg></app>室中作一水壇。或
<lb n="0424b12" ed="T"/><note n="0424038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">方或圓＝圓或方【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">方或圓【大】，圓或方【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424038"><lem wit="【大】">方或圓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">圓或方</rdg></app>各足一肘。以茅香甘松熏<note n="0424039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陸＋（白交）【甲】，（白）【乙】</note><note n="0424039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陸【大】，陸白交【甲】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->陸白【乙】</note><app n="0424039"><lem wit="【大】">陸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">陸白交</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">陸白</rdg></app>龍腦
<lb n="0424b13" ed="T"/>白檀五味和合泥塗之。其壇<note n="0424040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">場＝即【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0424040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">場【大】，即【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424040"><lem wit="【大】">場</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">即</rdg></app>內安著圓爐。
<lb n="0424b14" ed="T"/>飲食果子<note n="0424041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（七）＋分【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0424041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">分【大】，七分【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424041"><lem wit="【大】">分</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">七分</rdg></app>別置<note n="0424042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之燒＝燒之【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之燒【大】，燒之【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424042"><lem wit="【大】">之。燒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">燒之</rdg></app>食謂<note n="0424043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飯食＝粥飯腦【甲】，飯腦【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯食【大】，粥飯腦【甲】，飯腦【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424043"><lem wit="【大】">飯食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">粥飯腦</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">飯腦</rdg></app>果餅
<lb n="0424b15" ed="T"/><note n="0424044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">酥＝蘇【甲】【乙】＊</note><note n="0424044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">酥【大】＊，蘇【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0424044"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">蘇</rdg></app>蜜等。但五穀并乳木。隨人命星相<note n="0424045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">撿＝換【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">撿【大】，換【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424045"><lem wit="【大】">撿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">換</rdg></app>
<lb n="0424b16" ed="T"/>用之。</p>
<lb n="0424b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0424b1701">先啟詞曰　至心奉啟北極七<note n="0424046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔明〕－【甲】</note><note n="0424046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0424046"><lem wit="【大】">明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0424047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娜＝那【甲】，〔娜〕－【乙】</note><note n="0424047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娜【大】，那【甲】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0424047"><lem wit="【大】">娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">那</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>羅貪
<lb n="0424b18" ed="T"/><note n="0424048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔狼〕－【丙】</note><note n="0424048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狼【大】，〔－〕【丙】</note><app n="0424048"><lem wit="【大】">狼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0424049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">巨＝臣【乙】</note><note n="0424049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">巨【大】，臣【乙】</note><app n="0424049"><lem wit="【大】">巨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">臣</rdg></app>門祿存文曲廉貞武曲破軍尊星。為
<lb n="0424b19" ed="T"/><note n="0424050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陀＝施ヵ【原】，施【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0424050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陀【大】，施【考偽-原】，施【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424050"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">陀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">施</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">施</rdg></app>主<note n="0424051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">某甲二字甲乙二本作夾註</note><note n="0424051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">某甲【大】，(某甲)【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424051"><lem wit="【大】">某甲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><note place="inline">某甲</note></rdg></app>。災厄解脫壽命延長得見百秋。
<lb n="0424b20" ed="T"/>今作曼<note n="0424052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">荼＝茶【甲】</note><note n="0424052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">荼【大】，茶【甲】</note><app n="0424052"><lem wit="【大】">荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">茶</rdg></app>羅。唯願垂哀降臨此處。納受護
<lb n="0424b21" ed="T"/>摩。擁護施主<note n="0424053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">某甲二字甲乙二本作夾註</note><note n="0424053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">某甲【大】，(某甲)【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424053"><lem wit="【大】">某甲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><note place="inline">某甲</note></rdg></app>。災難解脫壽命增長所願
<lb n="0424b22" ed="T"/>從心<note place="inline">三<note n="0424054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍＝反【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0424054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遍【大】，反【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424054"><lem wit="【大】">遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">反</rdg></app></note>。</p>
<lb n="0424b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0424b2301">次結其印。虛心合掌。以二大指。捻二無名
<lb n="0424b24" ed="T"/>指甲。<note n="0424055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【丙】</note><note n="0424055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，〔－〕【丙】</note><app n="0424055"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>中指二小指如蓮葉。二頭指小開
<lb n="0424b25" ed="T"/>屈來去。</p>
<lb n="0424b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0424b2601">次誦一字頂輪王真言。并召北斗七星真言。</p>
<lb n="0424b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0424b2701">頂<note n="0424056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">輪＋（王）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輪【大】，輪王【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424056"><lem wit="【大】">輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">輪王</rdg></app>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0424b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0424b2801" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0424057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲乙丙三本俱梵字無之</note><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5A9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">曩</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5ED"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0424058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慕＝謨【甲】【乙】，莫【丙】</note><note n="0424058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慕【大】，謨【甲】【乙】，莫【丙】</note><app n="0424058"><lem wit="【大】">慕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">謨</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">莫</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A67A"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">三</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5E5"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">曼</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-CA56"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0424059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">多＝哆【甲】【乙】＊</note><note n="0424059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多【大】＊，哆【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0424059"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">哆</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A56F"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">那</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5FD"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">羅</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><note n="0424b2801" resp="CBETA" type="add"><g ref="#SD-A56F"/><g ref="#SD-A5FD"/>【CB】，<g ref="#SD-D957"/>【大】</note><app n="0424b2801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA"><g ref="#SD-A56F"/><g ref="#SD-A5FD"/></lem><rdg wit="【大】"><g ref="#SD-D957"/></rdg></app></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">那羅</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5B5"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0424060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跛＝破【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">跛【大】，破【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424060"><lem wit="【大】">跛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">破</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A47C"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">左</cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0424b29" ed="T"/>
<pb n="0424c" xml:id="T21.1306.0424c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424c01" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5FD"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0424061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【甲】【乙】＊</note><note n="0424061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】＊，羅【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0424061"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羅</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E17C"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">吽</cb:t></cb:tt></p>
<lb n="0424c02" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0424c0301">召北斗真言曰。</p>
