<lb n="0424c09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424c10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0424c1001">以手<note n="0424068" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">取＋（命）【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0424068" resp="CBETA" type="mod">取【大】，取命【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424068"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">取命</rdg></app>木及穀并<app type="star" corresp="#0424044"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">蘇</rdg></app><note n="0424069" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蜜＝密【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0424069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蜜【大】，密【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424069"><lem wit="【大】">蜜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">密</rdg></app>油等。擲之於爐內
<lb n="0424c11" ed="T"/>火燒之。<note n="0424070" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自＝目【甲】</note><note n="0424070" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自【大】，目【甲】</note><app n="0424070"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">目</rdg></app>專視其本命之星。若動搖變色。
<lb n="0424c12" ed="T"/><note n="0424071" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔光照通〕－【丙】</note><note n="0424071" resp="CBETA" type="mod">光照通【大】，〔－〕【丙】</note><app n="0424071"><lem wit="【大】">光<note n="0424072" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔照通〕－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0424072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">照通【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424072"><lem wit="【大】">照通</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>爍<note n="0424073" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光貌＝光色ヵ【原】，〔光貌〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424073" resp="CBETA" type="mod">光貌【大】，光色【考偽-原】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424073"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">光貌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">光色</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>黃白者。<note n="0424074" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＋（為）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424074" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即【大】，即為【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424074"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">即為</rdg></app>應願如<note n="0424075" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來＝未即【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424075" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來【大】，未即【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424075"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">未即</rdg></app>依
<lb n="0424c13" ed="T"/>前法七日夜而為之。必應如事不即其星藏
<lb n="0424c14" ed="T"/>沒不見<note place="inline">決云<note n="0424076" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不＋（可）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424076" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不【大】，不可【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424076"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">不可</rdg></app>求也</note>謂北斗七星者日月五星之精
<pb n="0425a" xml:id="T21.1306.0425a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0425a01" ed="T"/>也。曩括七曜照臨八方上曜於天神下直于
<lb n="0425a02" ed="T"/>人間。以司善惡而分禍福。群星所朝宗萬靈
<lb n="0425a03" ed="T"/>所俯仰。若有人能禮拜供養長壽福貴。不信
<lb n="0425a04" ed="T"/>敬者運命不久。是以祿命書云。世有司命神
<lb n="0425a05" ed="T"/>每至庚<note n="0425001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">申＝辛【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0425001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">申【大】，辛【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425001"><lem wit="【大】">申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">辛</rdg></app>日。上向天帝<note n="0425002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（所）＋陳【甲】</note><note n="0425002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陳【大】，所陳【甲】</note><app n="0425002"><lem wit="【大】">陳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">所陳</rdg></app>說眾人之罪惡。
<lb n="0425a06" ed="T"/>重罪者則<note n="0425003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">徹＝撤【甲】【乙】，擲【丙】</note><note n="0425003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">徹【大】，撤【甲】【乙】，擲【丙】</note><app n="0425003"><lem wit="【大】">徹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">撤</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">擲</rdg></app>算。輕罪者則去紀。算<note n="0425004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">書＝盡【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0425004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">書【大】，盡【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425004"><lem wit="【大】">書</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">盡</rdg></app>紀<note n="0425005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">告即主＝告即至【甲】，失即至【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0425005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告即主【大】，告即至【甲】，失即至【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425005"><lem wit="【大】">告
<lb n="0425a07" ed="T"/>即主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">告即至</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">失即至</rdg></app>命<note n="0425006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝亡最好ィ【原】，亡【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0425006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已【大】，亡最好【校異-原】，亡【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0425006"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">亡最好</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">亡</rdg></app>者。是故如來為末世薄福短命夭
<lb n="0425a08" ed="T"/>死眾生故。說是一字頂輪王召北斗七星供
<lb n="0425a09" ed="T"/>養護摩之儀則。為供養者。令其<note n="0425007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">屬命＝命屬【丙】</note><note n="0425007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">屬命【大】，命屬【丙】</note><app n="0425007"><lem wit="【大】">屬命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">命屬</rdg></app>星數削
<lb n="0425a10" ed="T"/>死籍還付生籍。若諸國王於自宮中作曼茶
<lb n="0425a11" ed="T"/>羅。如法護摩禮拜供養。北斗歡喜為擁護故。
<lb n="0425a12" ed="T"/>久居勝位恒受安穩。后妃夫人後宮<note n="0425008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">綵＝婇【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0425008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綵【大】，婇【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0425008"><lem wit="【大】">綵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">婇</rdg></app>女。王
<lb n="0425a13" ed="T"/>子群臣三公百官。上下和穆不行非法。人民
<lb n="0425a14" ed="T"/>熾盛稼穡豐饒國土安寧。無有災難不現<note n="0425009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怪異＝異怪【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0425009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怪異【大】，異怪【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0425009"><lem wit="【大】">怪
<lb n="0425a15" ed="T"/>異</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">異怪</rdg></app>。疫病死<note n="0425010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">亡＝市【乙】</note><note n="0425010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亡【大】，市【乙】</note><app n="0425010"><lem wit="【大】">亡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">市</rdg></app>不起。境內怨敵群賊自然退
<lb n="0425a16" ed="T"/>散。故以是法甚為祕要。</p>
<lb n="0425a17" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>北斗七<note n="0425011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">星＋（護摩）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0425011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">星【大】，星護摩【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425011"><lem wit="【大】">星</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">星護摩</rdg></app>祕要儀<note n="0425012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">軌＝則一卷【甲】</note><note n="0425012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">軌【大】，則一卷【甲】</note><app n="0425012"><lem wit="【大】">軌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">則一卷</rdg></app><note n="0425013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下甲本奧書云久安四年七月二十八日於高野奉傳受了，乙本奧書云（朱書）嘉承二年二月十三日於禪定房以御本移點了同日御房受奉了，一校了僧林寬之本，久安五年二月二十一日辰時許樂生房奉受了僧<g ref="#CB10923"/>信，丙本奧書云文和二年癸未二月二十七日申尅於神護寺成身院書寫畢宣澄二十四歲</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>